fields.body:
Welcome on Test site

This is a test page of OIDC plugins.

With this button, the provider transmits the user's data. However, the user will not be logged in.
This content is only visible to email verified users.

Test data handover

Show the request and the response details in Django messages.
Caution! Following Login via MojeID creates new user after succesfull login. To disable this feature turn on the switch "No new user".

Login via MojeID provider

This button allows the user to log in to the administration. If the user does not exist, it will be created. The creation of a new user can be switched off with the "No new user" switch in the plugin OIDC Login.

A newly created user has no permissions set. By overloading the function create_new_user overloading the DjangoOIDCAuthenticationBacked class, they can possibly be set.
